Output examples/gifs/web-search.gif

Set Height 760
Set Width 1400
Set Framerate 18
Set FontSize 26

Hide
  Type `export PATH="$PWD/examples/demo-bin:$PATH"; clear`
  Enter
  Sleep 300ms
Show

Sleep 500ms
Type@25ms `mods --web-search "What changed in the latest Go release?"`
Sleep 400ms
Enter
Sleep 5s
